summary: I loved this show as a kid, but I would always cry when Snufkin had to leave Moominvalley. Everything about him felt so...
body:
I loved this show as a kid, but I would always cry when Snufkin had to leave Moominvalley. Everything about him felt so mysterious~

Honestly, it’s such a chilled, slow-paced show.

There is also talk of a new 3D series of the Moomins coming out this year too~

(Plus, using charcoal & a white-inked pen is so much fun :))

blog.name: arlessiar
blog.title: The virtual life
blog.description: Arlessiar: female, German European. Working at the Kingsman tailor shop in Savile Row, on duty on a Federation starship, killing demons in Ferelden. Whump and h/c passion. Lots of other fandoms show up here every now and then, and lots of Colin Firth. Loving London and literature, poetry and photography. Trying to live by the principle of mindfulness. Coffee makes me happy, and orange is the most fantastic colour in the universe.
